
  Gothorita    Psychic Type Pokémon

  They use hypnosis to control 
  people and Pokémon.  Tales of 
  Gothorita leading people astray 
  are told in every corner. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Gothita ► Gothorita ► Gothitelle

